Abbreviation of [[geneva]].

====Noun====
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|-}}

#A [[colourless]] [[non]]-[[aged]] [[alcoholic]] [[liquor]] made by [[distilling]] [[ferment]]ed [[grain]]s such as [[barley]], [[corn]], [[oats]] or [[rye]] with [[Juniper]] [[berries]]; the [[base]] for many [[cocktail]]s
#[[Gin rummy]]

